{"tid":365723,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有offer但咁岩撞左返學應該點","createTime":"2017-08-19T12:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T19:43:59.000Z","uid":136972,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"699c7ca1a31c8ff18a8b4e1635b176d157cc63b5","tid":365723,"uid":136972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"話說我搵左份文職part time <br />\n岩岩收到offer叫星期一返工<br />\n同時 出左返學時間表<br />\n我係讀full time degree <br />\nAdd drop 難調到堂去返工<br />\n人地要求一星期夾埋要返到2日<br />\n但目前應該都係返到1.5日<br />\n不過仲要揀多一科<br />\n我就怕揀埋科後連果1.5日都冇埋<br />\n咁我應該直接星期一唔返工定返左先算"},{"pid":"1d0255b34dcedfba56d85851cf77c73b3209aba4","tid":365723,"uid":52566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"打去講囉on9"},{"pid":"eb77ac15e974edd1b03a997f8c7ffcfa36d7f13d","tid":365723,"uid":41250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"屌，咁想返工咪讀啦"},{"pid":"49b092b39279e2afe19fa1b150809b230442aada","tid":365723,"uid":2419,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"而家弱鳩智都讀到大學?"},{"pid":"dd991bfe6c9c2076b997d6c790e57e3679bb454c","tid":365723,"uid":32932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"個名改得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6e8469244870a2e152b4fe88d55810d521128c","tid":365723,"uid":136972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打去講囉on9</blockquote><br />\n咁公司星期六日冇人<br />\n又星期一返工"},{"pid":"7d29043847c7954323c81cdbc36cf838b71705c4","tid":365723,"uid":2671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"退學咪得囉"},{"pid":"f1cf2f668aec90bd71de4f81a18bfa65b9b1b3b8","tid":365723,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1