19T17:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打去講囉on9</blockquote><br />\n咁公司星期六日冇人<br />\n又星期一返工</blockquote><br />\n你呀頭冇比電話你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得公司電話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得你星期一預早反公司先<br />\n之後再同呀頭講請假再反學校<br />\n咁你又最少有付出左（有到/有份心）<br />\n咁條友會條氣順啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋第一日反工唔會叫你做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係比你睇下公司文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你怕醜既（假如公司人多）<br />\n你就更早反到公司企係office門口'步'個呀頭<br />\n<br />\n最緊要有份心話比人知：我想做呢份工喎<br />\n條友咁都嬲嬲豬既 搵個份算了吧⋯⋯"},{"pid":"d4a18cb3e8936b334ca5a2f997672150c4007299","tid":365723,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:15:50.000Z","msg":"有乜 Part time 咁特別"},{"pid":"d557a131d7a1c7775854c78a2a34146dcea0c258","tid":365723,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"讀大學都要將小事放上黎問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd8d58b6d2797559eeee170ae0c73fca2adf27e","tid":365723,"uid":97481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"請你個間公司都好奇怪 竟然唔問你一個禮拜返到邊幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfac63c500fa74ccdff6b153a9ce3ffe49b77920","tid":365723,"uid":17306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"而家真係咩人都讀到大學"},{"pid":"b8fc61732bdd866cfb6d5af7080192f14ef893eb","tid":365723,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有乜 Part time 咁特別</blockquote><br />\n可能係ibank嗰類"},{"pid":"6892e3bd88ea4fd0d2f662efca1e8fef80d7fb78","tid":365723,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:36:51.000Z","msg":"弱智都讀到大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec06a792a494a4b1074b316d5062b447a3519ffa","tid":3657